targets.query: select difference("write")/10000/60 as cluster_write_qps from (select sum("write") as "write" from (select last("fieldsWritten") AS "write" from $database..httpd WHERE $timeFilter group by time(1m),*  fill(linear)) group by time(1m) fill(linear)) limit 718 offset 1
select difference("bytes")/10 from (SELECT sum("writeReqBytes") AS "bytes" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null))
SELECT difference("fieldsWritten")/10000/10 FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE  $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname"
SELECT difference("WriteFieldsCount")/10000/10 FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname"
SELECT difference("writeReqBytesIn")/1024/1024/10 AS "mean_writeReqBytes" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY hostname
SELECT difference("writeReqBytes")/1024/1024/10 AS "mean_writeReqBytes" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY hostname
SELECT difference("snapshotBytes")/10 FROM $database.."io" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("writeReq")/10 AS "mean_writeReq" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname"
SELECT mean("writeReqActive") AS "mean_writeReqActive" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("fieldsWritten")/difference("writeReq") FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname"
SELECT WriteActiveRequests FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("writeReqDurationNs")/difference("writeReq") AS "Duration" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("WriteStorageDurationNs")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") AS "Duration" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("WriteGetTokenDurationNs")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") AS "Duration" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter group by hostname

panels.title: 计算数据量大小耗时（流控功能）

targets.query: SELECT difference("WriteIndexDurationNs")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") AS "Duration" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter group by hostname
SELECT difference("WriteRowsDurationNs")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") as "Duration" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter group by hostname
SELECT difference("WriteWalDurationNs")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") as "Duration" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter group by hostname
SELECT difference("WriteFieldsCount")/difference("WriteRowsBatch") as "FieldCount" FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY hostname
SELECT mean("agg_rows_last") AS "mean_agg_rows_last" FROM $database.."executor" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "app" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("pointsWrittenOK")/10 FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT difference("WriteRowsCount")/10 FROM $database.."performance" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname" FILL(null)
